        {
            "title": "CFA一級考試通過率維持在43% 高於十年平均水平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"CFA Institute\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"934\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iwnMM6i2sOaRXIvN.8R49w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTkzNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c69c2a352574751bbe1b04feb733c483\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">CFA Institute</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 特許金融分析師(CFA)考試一級通過率保持在歷史平均水平以上，而推遲過考試的考生的通過率仍然更低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CFA協會周二表示，11月，43%的考生通過了一級考試，與8月持平，但低於5月和2月的45%。這高於過去十年的平均通過率41%，並自2021年的低點以來已經回升，當時通過率受到新冠疫情期間考試推遲的影響。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"934\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NNNklUeEGD6FU1DxWVH3.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTkzNDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9c60811ee4dfb1e2cb60c450ecb32632\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推遲過考試的考生通過率更低。CFA協會稱，在11月參加一級考試且至少推遲過一次的考生，通過率為29%，而首次應考者的通過率為49%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-16b3e660-3fd6-3fc6-8553-c44570b44a5e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近2.7萬名考生11月在全球518個考試中心參加了一級考試。CFA考試在疫情期間從紙質過渡到機考。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：CFA一級考試通過率降至43% 而終級關卡卻被AI模型輕鬆拿捏</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">11月參加CFA二級考試的考生定於1月15日收到成績。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題CFA Level I Pass Rate Stays at 43%, Above Test’s Decade Average</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/cfa-%E7%B4%9A%E8%80%83%E8%A9%A6%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E7%8E%87%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%9C%A843-%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-162056442.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 01:26:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普為聯儲會調查風波再添一把火 批鮑威爾「要麼無能、要麼腐敗」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在司法部調查<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>引發軒然大波後，美國總統唐納德·川普指責聯儲會主席傑羅姆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>要麼「無能」，要麼「腐敗」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周二在離開白宮前往底特律時對記者表示：「他超預算了幾十億美元，要麼是無能，要麼就是腐敗。我不知道是哪一種，但顯然他干得並不好。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這項調查標志著川普政府對聯儲會的攻擊顯著升級，引發了對該機構獨立性的質疑。川普此前多次試探是否能在鮑威爾任期於5月結束前將其解職，目前他還在權衡提名誰作為下一任主席。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e43a4035-c8bb-38ba-a0b4-2833fdd6ad8d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普此前似乎試圖與這項調查保持距離，他曾對NBC新聞表示自己對這些傳票並不知情。川普長期以來批評鮑威爾，並多次要求聯儲會降息。他還表示，除非候選人承諾降息，否則不會任命新的主席，這一標準進一步動搖了聯儲會獨立性的根基。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾在周日的一份聲明中稱，這項翻修調查是施壓降息的「借口」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says Powell ‘Incompetent’ or ‘Crooked’ Amid Probe Furor</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%82%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E5%86%8D%E6%B7%BB-%E6%8A%8A%E7%81%AB-%E6%89%B9%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE-%E8%A6%81%E9%BA%BC%E7%84%A1%E8%83%BD-%E8%A6%81%E9%BA%BC%E8%85%90%E6%95%97-161519490.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 01:26:03",
